    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather and choose adventurers by using your math skills to grow your army in this auto-battler to defeat all enemies through the world of Calculon.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through the land while gathering adventurers and defeating enemies, move through the world to finally face the ogre king.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play challenge mode using multiple difficulty settings with an optional automatic difficulty adjustment. Try to set the highest scores in the leaderboards. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introducing additions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introducing subtractions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Subtractions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introducing multiplications</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplications</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introducing divisions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divisions</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022380/extras/56e2d8b2cb09351f0548a72c86d4a8f1.avif?t=1769164768\" width=395 height=348 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Multiplication math problem</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022380/extras/0cbc2fa835c29569173e4e7e89fa271f.avif?t=1769164768\" width=397 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Negative numbers in a math problem</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022380/extras/24493597da9915682048f52d82c37d88.avif?t=1769164768\" width=402 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Divisions</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022380/extras/41086bba1d68c548da2628bc2a663dbb.avif?t=1769164768\" width=493 height=683 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Higher difficulties can have free input and a timer</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your adventurers by acquiring skills. Improve their attack speed, damage and hitpoints with the skill point you earn by leveling up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022380/extras/bc751d651166f1a43a591224435b79e2.avif?t=1769164768\" width=427 height=515 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Achievements</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain achievements by recruiting adventurers, defeating enemies, completing levels and gathering experience to level up.</p>",
